#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/urathgarivarsson.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rathgar Ivarsson</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#660000>(3/25/02 3:28:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=477.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Deflection shields - work or not?</span><hr size=1> Shields add ac. So if the mob is hitting for minimum already, you will see no difference. Now if you see a mob hitting you for 106, 88, 124....then pop the shield and you will see it drop to minimum damage. <br><br>I personally use shields anytime a mob hits for more than minimum. A ql 55 ish shield will add about 1000ac.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uiccusion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>iccusion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#660000>(3/26/02 12:14:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=477.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Deflection shields - work or not?</span><hr size=1> Rathgar said:<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;I personally use shields anytime a mob hits for more than minimum. A ql 55 ish shield will add about 1000ac.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->But don't those things lock Parry?  So, you wouldn't be able to use BwT for another 5 minutes, right?  Is that worth it?<br><br>- Rookie Aidyl<br>51st Omni-Tek MA, RK1 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ucson777.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cson777</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 186<br> <font color=#660000>(3/26/02 12:35:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=477.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> no</span><hr size=1> BwT locks the MA skill for 40 seconds. The Deflection Shield locks Parry for 5 min. Two different things. Deflection Shields are a nice bonus. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#99CC66><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uiccusion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>iccusion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#660000>(3/26/02 3:17:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=477.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: no</span><hr size=1> cson said:<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> &quot;BwT locks the MA skill for 40 seconds. The Deflection Shield locks Parry for 5 min. Two different things. Deflection Shields are a nice bonus.&quot;<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Excellent!<br><br>Thanks for the info...since I use a Q85 BwT, I have loads of Parry, and even kept a nice Deflect Shield I found in a mission once.  Now I can use it without worrying about locking out my BwT attack!<br><br>- Rookie Aidyl<br>51st Omni-Tek MA, RK1 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uautumndawnfire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Autumn Dawnfire</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.melanierawn.com/images/bunnie.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 187<br> 